  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This trial is conducted in Asia. The aim of this trial is evaluate the remission rate in
      newly diagnosed subjects with type 2 diabetes after short-term intensive treatment with
      insulin aspart and insulin NPH.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
